---
title: "{{ title }}"
date: {{ date_iso }}
draft: false
tags:
{%- for topic in topics %}
  - {{ topic | replace('"', "'") | tojson }}
{%- endfor %}
levels:
{%- for level in active_levels %}
  - {{ level }}
{%- endfor %}
video_url: "{{ video_url }}"
audio_url: "{{ audio_url }}"
summary: "{{ topics[:3] | join('、') }}"
---

{% raw %}{{< media-player >}}{% endraw %}

<script type="application/json" id="segments-data">
{{ segments | tojson }}
</script>

## 📝 逐字稿 Transkript

<div class="transcript-table">

| 時間 | Deutsch | 中文翻譯 |
|:-----|:--------|:---------|
{%- for seg in segments %}
| <span class="ts-link" data-time="{{ seg.start }}">{{ seg.start }}</span> | {{ seg.de | replace("|", "｜") }} | {{ seg.zh | replace("|", "｜") }} |
{%- endfor %}

</div>

{% if active_levels %}
<div class="cefr-tabs">
{%- for level in active_levels %}
  <button class="cefr-tab{% if loop.first %} active{% endif %}" data-level="{{ level }}">{% if level == "A1" %}🟢 A1 初學{% elif level == "A2" %}🟡 A2 初級{% elif level == "B1" %}🔴 B1 中級{% endif %}</button>
{%- endfor %}
</div>
{% endif %}

{% if levels.get("A1") and (levels.A1.vocabulary or levels.A1.grammar or levels.A1.patterns) %}
<div class="cefr-content{% if "A1" == active_levels[0] %} active{% endif %}" data-level="A1">

### 🟢 A1 — 初學者區 Anfänger

{% if levels.A1.vocabulary %}
#### 📖 單字 Wortschatz

| 單字 | 詞性/冠詞 | 中文 | 例句 | 例句翻譯 |
|:-----|:----------|:-----|:-----|:---------|
{%- for v in levels.A1.vocabulary %}
| **{{ v.word }}** | {{ v.article or "" }} | {{ v.meaning }} | {{ v.example | replace("|", "｜") }} | {{ v.example_zh | replace("|", "｜") }} |
{%- endfor %}

{% endif %}
{% if levels.A1.grammar %}
#### 📝 文法 Grammatik

{% for g in levels.A1.grammar %}
<details>
<summary><strong>{{ g.rule }}</strong></summary>

> **德文**：{{ g.german }}
>
> **中文**：{{ g.chinese }}

{{ g.explanation }}

</details>

{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
{% if levels.A1.patterns %}
#### 💬 句型 Satzmuster

{% for p in levels.A1.patterns %}
- **{{ p.pattern }}**
  - 🇩🇪 {{ p.example }}
  - 🇹🇼 {{ p.translation }}
  - 💡 {{ p.note }}

{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

</div>
{% endif %}

